## How do you keep customers happy and achieve your business goals? Short answer: Its complicated.

The longer answer is that decisions in CPG organizations have become increasingly more complex as competition ramps up to meet the ever-evolving demands of socially-conscious, digitally-enabled consumers. This is a trend thats taking place across the board in business, as Gartner has noted:

